OL,3,CLiverpool call for investigation after
OL,4,Cyouth player 'racially abused' twice
OL,6,FLiverpool FC have called for an
OL,7,F"urgent and thorough investigation"
OL,8,Fafter saying a member of their under-
OL,9,F18s team was the victim of racial
OL,10,Fabuse in two matches in Germany.
OL,12,FPlayers and coaches left the pitch in
OL,13,Fboth fixtures, against Hoffenheim on
OL,14,FFriday and against Eintracht Frankfurt
OL,15,Fon Saturday, at the Bundesliga Cup
OL,16,Fyouth tournament.
OL,18,FThe same player complained to match
OL,19,Fofficials and coaches that he had been
OL,20,Fabused by players in the opposing
OL,21,Fteam. Both matches were abandoned.
