OL,6,F"In a further incident, the same
OL,7,Fplayer was the target of abuse during
OL,8,Fa fixture in the tournament (on
OL,9,FSaturday).
OL,11,F"Again, the player alerted his team-
OL,12,Fmates and coaching staff and our
OL,13,Fmanagement team opted to leave the
OL,14,Fpitch once more.
OL,16,F"We are proud of our player for his
OL,17,Fprompt actions in reporting the
OL,18,Fincident and the maturity of his
OL,19,Fresponse.
