OL,3,CLiverpool call for investigation after
OL,4,Cyouth player 'racially abused' twice
OL,6,F"He and any of his team-mates affected
OL,7,Fare being supported by the academy
OL,8,Fsafeguarding team.
OL,10,F"The club calls upon our opponents and
OL,11,Fthe tournament organisers to conduct
OL,12,Fan urgent and thorough investigation
OL,13,Finto the incident."
OL,15,FEintracht's sporting director Timmo
OL,16,FHardung told German newspaper Bild the
OL,17,Fclub took the accusation "seriously"
OL,18,Fbut insisted it had been a "linguistic
OL,19,Fissue" relating to a term that is
OL,20,Fcommonly used in Germany.
