OL,3,CLiverpool call for investigation after
OL,4,Cyouth player 'racially abused' twice
OL,6,F"Our entire youth academy is like
OL,7,FEintracht Frankfurt, multicultural and
OL,8,Fwe have clear values that we live by
OL,9,Fand demand again and again," Hardung
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Racism has no place here, but we
OL,13,Fstill take such an accusation
OL,14,Fseriously.
OL,16,F"We can rule out racism, it is a
OL,17,Flinguistic issue and therefore hope to
OL,18,Fhave resolved the misunderstanding
OL,19,Famong the players and Liverpool
OL,20,Fofficials concerned."
